    "title": "MSC India Advisory Limited is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "MSC India Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Warehouse Manager for our Mumbai operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout MSC India Advisory Limited:\nMSC India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MSC India Advisory Limited!",
